	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1" facs="EHRI-DR-19431213_01.jpg"/>
			<p>[…]</p>
			<p>On <date when="1943-12-01">December 1</date>, the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1068" type="subject"
					>Press</term> published a Circular of the Provincial Presidents, who now unite the posts as (administrative) Prefect and
				(political) <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1063" type="subject">Fascist</term> leader in the Province,
				by the following <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1119" type="subject">Police</term>
				<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-339" type="subject">Ordinance</term>:</p>
			<p>1) All <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term>, including those occupying a
				special position of any <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1147" type="subject">nationality</term> residing
				in <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-486">Italy</orgName>, must be put in <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-496" type="subject">concentration camps</term>.</p>
			<p>All their <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-887" type="subject">property</term>, movable property, and
				immovable property will be seized immediately until they can be <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-585"
					type="subject">confiscated</term> for the benefit of the <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-486"
					>Social Italian Republic</orgName>, which will use them to the best for the casualties of the hostile <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1105" type="subject">airstrikes</term>.</p>
			<p>All those who are offspring of a <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-375" type="subject">mixed
					Marriage</term>, are recognized under applicable <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-486"
					>Italian</orgName>
				<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-365" type="subject">Racial Law</term> as of <pb n="2"
					facs="EHRI-DR-19431213_02.jpg"/>
				<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-373" type="subject">Aryan</term> descent and must be placed under
				special <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1122" type="subject">police supervision</term>.</p>
			<p>With regard to the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1068" type="subject">Press’s</term> comments on these
				new <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-339" type="subject">Regulations</term>, one is permitted to state
				the following; <q>REGIME FASCISTA</q> on the <date when="1943-12-02">2 December</date> seeks to justify the new Precautions against
				the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term>, by stating first, that <orgName
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-486">Italian</orgName>
				<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> under <persName
					ref="#ehri_dr_badoglio_pietro">Badoglio's</persName>
				<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-948" type="subject">government</term> were active in an <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-967" type="subject">anti-fascist</term> movement, and participated in the
				destruction of fascist property, etc. and that before the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1080"
					type="subject">war</term> - as is evident from various texts quoted - sought to instigate. There is thus no doubt about their
				responsibility. The logical answer is that we should <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-529" type="subject"
					>exterminate</term> the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term>. But, as
				always, the <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-486">Italian</orgName> people appear extremely noble and
				have confined themselves to <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-660" type="subject">robbing</term> them of
				their possessions. The <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1083" type="subject">bombing</term> of our cities
				is wanted and praised by the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-309" type="subject">Jewish
					International</term>. What is more reasonable than their possessions being used, to relieve the consequences of the Hebrew crime
				to some degree?</p>
			<p>[…]</p>
			<pb n="4" facs="EHRI-DR-19431213_03.jpg"/>
			<p><placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3174659/livorno.html">Livorno</placeName> magazine <q>TELEGRAFO</q> on the <date
					when="1943-12-08">8/12</date> publishes a Note, dated <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3169070/rome.html">Rome</placeName>,
					<date when="1943-12-07">7/12</date>, of the following: Only twelve hours after the republican-<term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1063" type="subject">fascist</term>
				<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-948" type="subject">government</term> had decreed that the <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> should be <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-529" type="subject">eliminated</term> from the life of the <orgName
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-486">Italian</orgName> state, the capital has begun the process of
				purification. <pb n="5" facs="EHRI-DR-19431213_04.jpg"/> In total, 10,000 Persons of <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Semitic</term> descent have been chased out. Some of
				the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> of <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/3169070/rome.html">Rome</placeName> have already left the city some time ago and set off for northern
					<orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-486">Italy</orgName>. It is expected that in this way approx.
				20,000 apartments, will be made available for injured <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3169070/rome.html">Roman</placeName>
				families and for refugees from southern <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-486">Italy</orgName>.</p>
			<p>However, the <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3169070/rome.html">Roman</placeName>
				<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-711" type="subject">magazines</term> did not contain any such message,
				just as the legation have not heard anything to confirm this.</p>
			<p><persName ref="#ehri_dr_wadsted_otto">Otto Wadsted</persName></p>
